'''NEXUS'''是[[美国|美国]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]联合运作的一种快速入境通关计划，可以让预先通过审查的低风险旅客在美、加之间的旅行时，在机场、港口或陆路口岸享受快速通道。<ref name = "forbes">{{Cite web | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/marcwebertobias/2014/09/02/global-entry-and-nexus-passes-what-you-need-to-know-to-keep-them-valid | title = Global Entry and Nexus Passes: What You Need to Know to Keep Them Valid | publisher = [[福布斯|福布斯]] | accessdate = 2019-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191216043023/https://www.forbes.com/sites/marcwebertobias/2014/09/02/global-entry-and-nexus-passes-what-you-need-to-know-to-keep-them-valid | dead-url = no }}</ref>符合条件的NEXUS计划参与者在美加机场还能享受快速安检服务。<ref name="cbsa">{{Cite web | url = http://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/menu-eng.html | title = NEXUS | publisher = [[加拿大边境服务局|加拿大边境服务局]] | accessdate = 2017-07-22 | archive-date = 2017-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170719052500/http://cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/menu-eng.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="cbp">{{Cite web |url = https://www.cbp.gov/travel/trusted-traveler-programs/nexus |title = NEXUS |publisher = [[美国海关及边境保卫局|美国海关及边境保卫局]] |accessdate = 2010-10-04 |archive-date = 2014-03-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140315084929/http://www.cbp.gov/travel/trusted-traveler-programs/nexus |dead-url = no }}</ref>其证件俗称'''芳邻卡'''，<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.yvr.ca/zh-cn/passengers/navigate-yvr/customs-and-immigration/canada-border-services-agency/canada-border-clearance | title = 自动入境通关、芳邻卡（NEXUS）和快速通关卡（CANPASS Air） | publisher = [[温哥华国际机场|温哥华国际机场]] | accessdate = 2017-07-22 | archive-date = 2017-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170711191707/http://www.yvr.ca/zh-cn/passengers/navigate-yvr/customs-and-immigration/canada-border-services-agency/canada-border-clearance | dead-url = no }}</ref>符合[[真实身份法案|真实身份]]（REAL ID）要求，在两国机场均被接受作为合法登机证件。NEXUS是[[美国国土安全部|美国国土安全部]]受信任旅客计划的一部分。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://ttp.dhs.gov/ | title = Official Trusted Traveler 