在通过背景审查和面试之后，即可获寄卡片，上网激活后即可在入境或登机安检时使用。通常申请者需要在申请前在美加其中一国住满三年时间。目前这一规定对两国部分公民已经取消，以便让居住在海外的美、加公民回国之后能立即申请参与NEXUS计划。但是两国的永久居民仍然需要在两国之一合法居住三年后方可提交申请。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://berardiimmigrationlaw.com/cbp-announces-lifting-of-three-year-residency-rule-for-canadian-citizen-nexus-applicants/ | title = CBP Announces Lifting of Three-Year Residency Rule for Canadian Citizen NEXUS Applicants | publisher = Berardi Immigration Law | accessdate = 2020-06-18 | archive-date = 2020-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200622021543/https://berardiimmigrationlaw.com/cbp-announces-lifting-of-three-year-residency-rule-for-canadian-citizen-nexus-applicants/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

申请者只能通过[[美国海关及边境保卫局|美国海关及边境保卫局]]的网站提交申请，申请费用为50美元。<ref name = "washingtonpost">{{Cite web | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/travel/from-passport-cards-to-global-entry-which-trusted-traveler-program-is-right-for-you/2017/05/11/1a5d816a-31e1-11e7-8674-437ddb6e813e_story.html | title = From passport cards to Global Entry, which trusted-traveler program is right for you? | publisher = [[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]] | accessdate = 2019-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191216142846/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/travel/from-passport-cards-to-global-entry-which-trusted-traveler-program-is-right-for-you/2017/05/11/1a5d816a-31e1-11e7-8674-437ddb6e813e_story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>申请者需要提供护照或签证信息，以保证能合法进入这两个国家。申请者还要在申请系统里填写过去五年居住地址以及工作信息。如果申请者年龄不足18岁，可以豁免申请费，不过其父母必须提交书面文件认可申请。<ref name = "join-nexus">{{cite web|url=https://www.cbp.gov/travel/trusted-traveler-programs/nexus/how-apply|publisher=[[美国海关及边境保卫局|美国海关及边境保卫局]]|title=How to Apply|accessdate=2017-07-22|archive-date=2017-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717121135/https://www.cbp.gov/travel/trusted-traveler-programs/nexus/how-apply|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/application-demande-eng.html|publisher=[[加拿大边境服务局|加拿大边境服务局]]|title=Join NEXUS|accessdate=2017-07-22|archive-date=2017-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723232355/http://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/application-demande-eng.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

收到申请材料后，[[美国国土安全部|美国国土安全部]]会审查申请者的国籍和移民身份，并在美国和加拿大分别对申请者进行背景调查，检查申请者是否有犯罪记录或与恐怖主义组织有关。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://chatnewstoday.ca/2019/01/10/u-s-government-shutdown-causing-delays-for-nexus-card-applications/ | title = U.S. Government shutdown causing delays for NEXUS card applications | publisher = CHAT News Today | accessdate = 2019-12-15}}</ref>通过初步筛选的申请者会收到面谈邀请，前往预约的机构接受美国海关及边境保卫局和加拿大边境服务局官员的面试。申请得到批准后，申请者会在不久之后收到邮寄的NEXUS卡片。该卡自申请者收到卡片之后的那个生日开始，有效期为5年。换新卡通常需要在旧卡失效前6个月时进行，申请者可能需要再次进行类似的面试，官员会决定持卡人是否还符合NEXUS的条件。<ref name = "join-nexus"/>

== 使用 ==
[[File:NexusLane.JPG|thumb]]（位于密歇根州、安大略省之间）口岸的NEXUS车道]]
NEXUS卡是符合[[西半球旅行计划|西半球旅行计划]]的旅行文件，<ref name = "cbsa-faq">{{cite web|title=Frequently Asked Questions about the NEXUS Program|url=http://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/faq-eng.html|publisher=[[加拿大边境服务局|加拿大边境服务局]]|accessdate=2017-07-22|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730141851/http://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/prog/nexus/faq-eng.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>可以被旅行者用作替代护照的证件通过已安装相关设备的美国和加拿大机场、边境口岸往返美国和加拿大。不过如果持卡人从其他国家抵达美国或加拿大，或是两国永久居民，则必须携带护照。<ref>{{cite web|title=WHTI Program Background|url=http://www.cbp.gov/travel/us-citizens/whti-program-background|publisher=[[美国海关及边境保卫局|美国海关及边境保卫局]]|accessdate=2017-07-22|archive-date=2015-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813140437/http://www.cbp.gov/travel/us-citizens/whti-program-background|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 陆路口岸 ===
NEXUS计划参与者可使用[[美加边境|美加边境]]陆路口岸的专用车道过境。大多数参与NEXUS项目的{{Link-en|美加陆路边境口岸|List of Canada–United States border crossings}}一般都至少有一条专门为NEXUS计划参与者保留的快速通道。<ref name = "nytimes">{{Cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/20/business/which-trusted-traveler-program-is-right-for-you.html | title = Which ‘Trusted Traveler’ Program Is Right for You? | publisher = [[纽约时报|纽约时报]] | accessdate = 2019-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191216043044/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/20/business/which-trusted-traveler-program-is-right-for-you.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>专用通道设有NEXUS读卡器，可以识别旅客身份。在陆路口岸，如果车辆上所有乘客（包括儿童）均为NEXUS计划参与者，并且车辆上未装载需要特殊报关手续的货物，这辆车方可以使用专用的NEXUS车道。NEXUS计划参与者通常可以比一般旅客在通过边境时花费更少的时间。不过仍然有可能接受常规的移民和海关检查，甚至被要求接受更仔细的[[二次安检_(美国)|二次检查]]（secondary screening）。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://buffalonews.com/2019/11/26/at-the-border-youre-likely-part-of-the-99-percent-inspectors-have-one-chance-to-be-sure/ | title = You're likely part of the 99%. Border agents get one chance to be sure. | publisher = Buffalo News | accessdate = 2019-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191216043026/https://buffalonews.com/2019/11/26/at-the-border-youre-likely-part-of-the-99-percent-inspectors-have-one-chance-to-be-sure/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 港口 ===
NEXUS计划参与者驾驶私人船舶穿越美加边境时，只需要通过电话在抵达前向[[美国海关和边境保护局|美国海关和边境保护局]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.cbp.gov/travel/pleasure-boats-private-flyers/pleasure-boat-overview | title = Pleasure Boat Reporting Requirements | publisher = [[美国海关和边境保护局|美国海关和边境保护局]] | accessdate = 2019-12-13 | archive-date = 2019-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213052048/https://www.cbp.gov/travel/pleasure-boats-private-flyers/pleasure-boat-overview | dead-url = no }}</ref>或[[加拿大边境服务局|加拿大边境服务局]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/travel-voyage/pb-pp-eng.html | title = Reporting requirements for private boaters | publisher = [[加拿大边境服务局|加拿大边境服务局]] | accessdate = 2019-12-13 | archive-date = 2019-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213052037/https://www.cbsa-asfc.gc.ca/travel-voyage/pb-pp-eng.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>进行申报。

